6. Love my mom and dad. They are tha best that i could ever asked for. Love my lil bro and big sis too.

8. Love Jazz, Fusion, Funk, Bossa, Samba, Gospel, Bebop, and J-Rock.

9. Self-proclaimed Petit Pettanko complex.

10.  Love my Dachshund, Norton :3

12. Animal Lovers since i was a baby. 
13. ANTI-MAINSTREAM GUY. Lots of stupid hobbies.. 14. Jones level tinggi. Former Secret Admirer.

Alvin, Mario, Adi, Eboen, Christo, Maw, William, Epil, Shu2.
And new friends that makes my life even better...
Kolonica, Tiffy, Acel, Eveline, Gaby, Inka, Chen2.

16. Grateful for what you have. Forgive your enemies. 
17. Love and Hate my hair at the same time. 
18. Want to be an Indie Game Developer, or a Visual Novel Maker. Side-job should be playing music.
